      <title>はじまるよ~博客搭建日志 4</title>
      <link href="/2022/12/08/%E3%81%AF%E3%81%98%E3%81%BE%E3%82%8B%E3%82%88-4/"/>
      <url>/2022/12/08/%E3%81%AF%E3%81%98%E3%81%BE%E3%82%8B%E3%82%88-4/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p>今天梓喵也<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/bangumi/play/ep21265">晕了</a></p><span id="more"></span><!-- 简单示例 (id, server, type)  -->    <div id="aplayer-WSMKuioY" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker"         data-id="2420303" data-server="netease" data-type="album" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="false" data-mutex="true" data-listmaxheight="340px" data-preload="auto" data-theme="#ad7a86"    ></div><p>论文整理完毕就等投稿，又抽空回来折腾一下blog</p><h2 id="不蒜子访问计数"><a href="#不蒜子访问计数" class="headerlink" title="不蒜子访问计数"></a>不蒜子访问计数</h2><p>使用非常非常简单的，参见<a href="http://ibruce.info/2015/04/04/busuanzi/">主页</a>。几乎不用怎么修改。<br>还是直接在主题文件<code>\layout\_partial\header.ejs</code>修改就行，在<code>&lt;div class=&quot;nexmoe-copyright&quot;&gt;</code>下加调用。</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">span</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;busuanzi_container_site_pv&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">span</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;busuanzi_value_site_pv&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">span</span>&gt;</span> views from <br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">span</span>&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">span</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;busuanzi_container_site_uv&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">span</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;busuanzi_value_site_uv&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">span</span>&gt;</span> persons <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">br</span>&gt;</span> <br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">span</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>函数<code>script</code>丢最后面</p><h2 id="评论系统"><a href="#评论系统" class="headerlink" title="评论系统"></a>评论系统</h2><p>发现waline做得挺好，也不需要登录就能评论，还有详尽的<a href="https://waline.js.org/guide/get-started/">官方文档</a>。<br>完成在waline上的配置后，需要在hexo里引入。<br>首先还是在主题文件<code>\layout\_partial\header.ejs</code>引入waline的渲染文件css，直接把代码插入<code>&lt;head&gt;</code>里面</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">head</span>&gt;</span><br><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- ... --&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">link</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">    <span class="hljs-attr">rel</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">    <span class="hljs-attr">href</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://unpkg.com/@waline/client@v2/dist/waline.css&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">  /&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- ... --&gt;</span><br>  <br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">head</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再把<code>post.ejs</code>，<code>py.ejs</code>，<code>plain.ejs</code>里的<code>page.comments</code>中间原来的执行代码替换一下，主题默认的评论系统还没有做，不起作用。<br>（plain不知道是控制哪个页面的，暂且都加上）</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml">&lt;% if (page.comments)&#123; %&gt;<br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;waline&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">script</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;module&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-javascript"></span><br><span class="language-javascript">    <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> &#123; init &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;https://unpkg.com/@waline/client@v2/dist/waline.mjs&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="language-javascript"></span><br><span class="language-javascript">    <span class="hljs-title function_">init</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="language-javascript">      <span class="hljs-attr">el</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;#waline&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="language-javascript">      <span class="hljs-attr">serverURL</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;https://your-domain.vercel.app&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="language-javascript">    &#125;);</span><br><span class="language-javascript">  </span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span> <br>&lt;% &#125; %&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>大功告成！挺好用！</p><h2 id="访问统计"><a href="#访问统计" class="headerlink" title="访问统计"></a>访问统计</h2><p>虽然通过google analytics认证添加了google索引，但是似乎还没有被更新进索引库里，用google还是搜不到这个网站，可能是链接太少了吧，多去搞搞友链说不定可以的，也去自己其他平台上放一下这个链接。<br>不得不说google analytics看着挺方便的，网站数据都能一览无余。</p><h2 id="Task-list"><a href="#Task-list" class="headerlink" title="Task list"></a>Task list</h2><ul><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>代码高亮：有点问题，暂且蒙古里（虽然我并一定会写很多代码</del> <a href="https://nantekoto.github.io/2022/11/30/%E3%81%AF%E3%81%98%E3%81%BE%E3%82%8B%E3%82%88-2/">↓解决鸟↓</a><ul><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>首行缩进</del></li></ul></li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>social模块：</del><ul><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>这个主题我唯一想换掉的就是左下角github的图标，太憨憨了（文档提供了方法</del></li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>一些额外的个人链接想要加上，要摸索下</del></li></ul></li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>建站时间</del> <a href="https://nantekoto.github.io/2022/12/01/%E3%81%AF%E3%81%98%E3%81%BE%E3%82%8B%E3%82%88-3/">↓解决鸟↓</a></li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>网站索引：要去google和baidu上登记一下（争取一点微弱的曝光量</del></li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>访问统计：用了不蒜子。</del><a href="https://nantekoto.github.io/2022/12/08/%E3%81%AF%E3%81%98%E3%81%BE%E3%82%8B%E3%82%88-4/">↓解决鸟↓</a></li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>评论插件：感觉都不好用，可能不会装（装了waline）</del></li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 本地搜索：可能会加？也可能懒得弄了</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 关于博主：可能这个模块才是比较重要的吧，有点懒，想写成CV的样子又觉得该随意点</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 个人域名：又要花钱，花钱的事最后再说</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Latex支持：latex公式写着很有意思，虽然我肯定不会在博客写，但说不定会装上</li></ul><p>又要忙报告，之后再说啦，<em>じゃあ~</em></p>]]></content>
      
      
